{"tid":466744,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩公司係睇工作能力 唔睇經驗？","createTime":"2017-11-13T00:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T01:56:54.000Z","uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"18097327af6d0dd9be21ee8dc76bdf138c6ca4e3","tid":466744,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:33:59.000Z","msg":"小弟 做文員既<br />\n第一份工係合約工<br />\n咁我好好彩<br />\n有人賞識 做左8個幾月就升左做perm<br />\n（對上好似我咁既例子 都做左年幾先升）<br />\n<br />\n問題黎喇 因為我大公司<br />\n遲過某個月join （計轉perm)<br />\n我下年無人工加 無bonus <br />\n<br />\n唔好講升職...<br />\n對上升果個轉左年幾都未再升<br />\n<br />\n所以我係到諗 如果有公司唔睇經驗<br />\n睇工作能力就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 由pt到ft 好多人欣賞我<br />\n無論係工作能力 人際關係等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我應該做夠1年定跳槽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n（最近學野學到好大壓力<br />\n    人地Manager職位要做既野 老細要我學曬<br />\n    但人地人工係我4倍<br />\n    我老細 要我做十完十美 <br />\n    好多野 得一兩個人識 都要我學曬<br />\n    到我學曬 掂...<br />\n    但因為經驗太淺..人工低）"},{"pid":"71ae104a65a8e836f76ff59e59a850c11fa58e43","tid":466744,"uid":4896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:16:13.000Z","msg":"咁經驗反映部分能力<br />\n好多task project 要run過幾年先識晒點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然好多純粹做左果個位十幾廿年 冇特別優勝點<br />\n高人幾倍人工就真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236c38410bd071b1a974c5156623c2e037f193e4","tid":466744,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:22:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁經驗反映部分能力<br />\n好多task project 要run過幾年先識晒點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然好多純粹做左果個位十幾廿年 冇特別優勝點<br />\n高人幾倍人工就真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但每間公司都唔同運作<br />\n每次入新公司都要學好多野<br />\n咁經驗真係好重要？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋 無野係學得識曬<br />\n<br />\n我會咁諗 係因為公司成日玩innovations..."},{"pid":"bb07094b0c1acbb54e9cab8a35573e193a30bb66","tid":466744,"uid":48277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:34:22.000Z","msg":"文員想升職？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c2f687cc19adebff3dbb1331daa9e48c0ec06e","tid":466744,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:38:59.000Z","msg":"你開間咪係囉"},{"pid":"66f28a513610ea9e5ced55a0fab447b16afb19ab","tid":466744,"uid":54142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:45:16.000Z","msg":"做老闆咪得得"},{"pid":"47193116a15a9b54fcd55f40b8d982973f351c97","tid":466744,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:47:24.000Z","msg":"Commission based jobs"},{"pid":"896bce27b62a7ee6a2991e41cb936b1753c45b6b","tid":466744,"uid":28054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:52:33.000Z","msg":"你係咪搞笑呀 做文員做到以為自己工作能力好掂<br />\n洗唔洗即刻升你做manager<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d27441993cf4601f9c2f74f755e523368ca89c","tid":466744,"uid":5690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:56:54.000Z","msg":"政府工"}]}